---
import ThemedImage from '@/components/common/ThemedImage';
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-4xl flex-col-reverse gap-x-3 px-4 sm:flex-row">
    <div class="flex w-full flex-col justify-center text-center sm:text-left">
      <h1 class="mb-3 text-3xl font-bold md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">
        Hi, I'm<br class="hidden sm:block" />
        <span class="text-accent">Kotaro Komori</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4 text-sm sm:mb-6 md:text-base">
        モダンなウェブ技術を使用して、美しく機能的なウェブサイトとアプリケーションを作成します。
      </p>
      <div
        class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-x-2 text-sm font-medium sm:justify-start sm:gap-x-3"
      >
        <a href="/about" class="flex rounded-lg bg-secondary px-6 py-3 shadow-lg hover:opacity-80">
          About Me
        </a>
        <a
          href="/works"
          class="rounded-lg bg-accent px-7 py-3 text-white shadow-lg hover:opacity-80"
        >
          Works
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <ThemedImage
      client:load
      lightThemeImageSrc="/assets/hello-light.svg"
      darkThemeImageSrc="/assets/hello-dark.svg"
      alt="Hello"
      width="384"
      height="384"
      className="mx-auto h-60 w-60 md:h-96 md:w-96"
    />
  </div>
</section>
